        &lt;State University of New York, Korea Undergraduate Student Council&gt; (hereinafter USC) follows the terms and agreements set by the “Personal Information Protection Act” in order to protect users’ personal information and their rights and interests and to handle user predicaments if necessary. If USC decides to amend the privacy policy, it will be announced (separately) on this website.     o This policy takes into effect as of February 14th, 2021. 
